Spec: Task States Sampler

Purpose:
  Exercises every TaskState symbol with and without IDs.

Tasks:
  [ ] open task without id
  [x] done task without id
  [-] skipped task without id
  [!] blocked task without id
  [?] needs-decision task without id
  [ ] #1 open with id one
  [x] #2 done with id two
  [!] #42 blocked with id forty-two
  [-] #100 skipped with id one-hundred
